'''Vader's Castle''' was a battlefield within the [[Grand Arena]] on [[Vespaara]]. It was based on [[Fortress Vader]] on [[Mustafar]].<ref name="Hunters" />

{{Struct-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
{{Quote|The Hunters Team had an absolute blast letting our imaginations run wild to create the unique environment of this battlefield. We hope you'll have a great time battling through the halls of Vader's Castle - keep your eyes peeled for even more secrets hidden within!|''Star Wars: Hunters'' Developers|<ref name="Vaders Castle Post">{{Hunters|url=news/enter-vader-s-castle-if-you-dare|text=Enter Vader's Castle&hellip;If You Dare!}}</ref>}}
Vader's Castle was first introduced in the [[canon]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] ''[[Star Wars: Hunters]]'' as one of its playable maps, which was developed by [[NaturalMotion]]'s [[BossAlien]]<ref name="Hunters" /> and initially published by [[Zynga]] on [[November 16]], [[2021]] as a [[Wikipedia:Soft launch|soft launch]]<ref name="Soft">{{Twitter|ZyngaStarWars|status/1460656552734605317|[[Zynga]] Star Wars|date=2021-11-16|quote=We are excited to announce Star Wars: Hunters is now entering soft launch and is available on Android for players in India, Philippines, Malaysia & Indonesia.|archiveurl=https://archive.ph/InyRJ|archivefile=File:ZyngaStarWars-SoftLaunchDate-Twitter.png}}</ref> before the global release on [[June 4]], [[2024]].<ref name="Global">{{SWYouTube|4dZcq6m3y40|Star Wars: Hunters Launch Date Reveal Trailer}}</ref> The map was added as part of the game's second season "Empire Resurgent" on [[August 1]], 2024.<ref name="S2 Roadmap">{{Twitter|ZyngaStarWars|status/1819025300212109614|[[Zynga]] ''Star Wars''|date=2024-08-01|quote=Season 2 'Empire Resurgent' is LIVE!|archiveurl=https://ghostarchive.org/archive/RSz7F|archivefile=File:ZyngaStarWars-HuntersSeason2Roadmap-Twitter.png}}</ref> Prior to its proper introduction, the map was briefly shown in the game's launch date reveal trailer.<ref name="Launch Trailer">{{SWYouTube|4dZcq6m3y40|Star Wars: Hunters Launch Date Reveal Trailer}}</ref> The battlefield was also first identified as Vader's Castle in the official patch notes on [[July 30]] of the same year.<ref name="S2 Patch">{{Hunters|url=news/k-a0s-arrives-in-season-2-empire-resurgent|text=K-A0S Arrives in Season 2: Empire Resurgent}}</ref>[[Wikipedia:Artist|Artist]] [[Clint Young]] was responsible for the location's early concept visualizations.<ref name="Concept ArtStation">{{ArtStation|subdomain=clintyoung|url=projects/wr4loX|name=[[Clint Young]]|text=Star Wars Hunters: Mustafar Vis Dev- exploration|date=2025-05-20|quote=Previs for Star Wars: Huntres- The Planet Mustafar and the Hunters Games broadcast arenas. These were a few of the visual designs and biomes pieces I completed for the game. Mustafar Arena early exploration - fight from outside castle to interior. capture Vader Holo. comm. * map call out included.|archivefile=File:ClintYoung-PrevisVadersCastle-ArtStation.png}}</ref>

